    "## Comparison Operators\n",
    "\n",
    "Comparison operators are used to compare two values:\n",
    "\n",
    "| Operator | Name | Example |\n",
    "| --- | --- | --- |\n",
    "| == | Equal | x == y |\n",
    "| != | Not equal | x != y |\n",
    "| > | Greater than | x > y |\n",
    "| < | Less than | x < y |\n",
    "| >= | Greater than or equal to | x >= y |\n",
    "| <= | Less than or equal to | x <= y |"
